text: John Anthony Olszewski Jr. ( ; born September 10, 1982), also known by his nickname Johnny O, is an American politician. He has been a member of the U.S. House of Representatives from Maryland's 2nd congressional district since 2025. He is a member of the Democratic Party. He was the 14th county executive of Baltimore County, Maryland, from 2018 to 2025. ==References== ==Other websites== * * * * Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from Maryland Category:Politicians from Baltimore Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
